title: Dating Horror Stories
overview: Dating Horror Stories is a fresh digital sketch show from Comedy Central UK, blending humour with social commentary on modern dating. Fronted by rising comedic star Kyrah Gray, each episode revolves around the experiences of a single Black woman and the stereotypes and anxieties associated with dating in the 21st-century. Celebrity Cameos include Munya Chawawa, Kiell Smith-Bynoe and Ola Labib.Â
